        <!-- =========================================
             PAGE 5: ANALYSIS & REQUIREMENTS PAGE
             ========================================= -->
        <section id="page-project-analysis" class="portfolio-page">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="subtitle">System Engineering</span>
                <h2>Analysis & Requirements</h2>
            </div>

            <h3 style="font-size:1.6rem; color:var(--accent-orange); margin-bottom:1rem;">Problem Statement</h3>
            <p class="bio-text-para" style="font-size:1.15rem;">
                Local CCTV businesses in Hubbali had no digital presence. Customers had to visit in person to know product availability and pricing. The owner managed a 400+ SKU inventory in an Excel sheet with no way to share it digitally.
            </p>

            <h3 style="font-size:1.6rem; color:var(--accent-orange); margin-top:3rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Stakeholder Taxonomy</h3>
            <div class="stakeholders-row">
                <div class="neon-card stakeholder-card">
                    <span class="stakeholder-card-icon">💼</span>
                    <h4>Business Owner</h4>
                    <p>Needs direct inventory tracking, quick SKU adjustments, and visual layouts to capture local Hubbali leads.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="neon-card stakeholder-card">
                    <span class="stakeholder-card-icon">👤</span>
                    <h4>End Customers</h4>
                    <p>Demand fast catalog filtering, product specs, dynamic cart building, and quick ways to reach the merchant.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="neon-card stakeholder-card">
                    <span class="stakeholder-card-icon">🔑</span>
                    <h4>Site Admin</h4>
                    <p>Requires secure, access-controlled endpoints to execute catalog CRUD items and manage dynamic parameters.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 style="font-size:1.6rem; color:var(--accent-orange); margin-bottom:1rem;">Functional Specifications</h3>
            <div class="glass-table-wrapper">
                <table class="glass-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>ID</th>
                            <th>Target Functional Requirement</th>
                            <th>Priority</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR1</td>
                            <td>Browse 400+ products classified in 12 distinct category boards</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-high">High</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR2</td>
                            <td>Filter options by brand, indoor/outdoor use, and camera resolutions</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-high">High</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR3</td>
                            <td>Interactive product specs panel with user rating averages</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-high">High</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR4</td>
                            <td>Cart tracker enabling customized packages calculation</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-high">High</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR5</td>
                            <td>Protected Merchant Portal and complete CRUD products management</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-high">High</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR6</td>
                            <td>Customer login integration utilizing secure Google OAuth credentials</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-medium">Medium</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR7</td>
                            <td>Instant WhatsApp trigger sharing product specifications</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-medium">Medium</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR8</td>
                            <td>Side-by-side comparison matrices mapping up to 3 individual items</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-medium">Medium</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>FR9</td>
                            <td>Global parameters editable dynamically from merchant settings</td>
                            <td><span class="priority-indicator priority-low">Low</span></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <h3 style="font-size:1.6rem; color:var(--accent-orange); margin-bottom:1rem;">Non-Functional Specifications</h3>
            <div class="timeline-steps" style="margin-top:2rem; margin-bottom:4rem;">
                <div class="neon-card">
                    <h4 style="color:var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">⚡ Performance</h4>
                    <p>Initial paint of the product catalog should load in under 2 seconds using server caching strategies.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="neon-card">
                    <h4 style="color:var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">📈 Scalability</h4>
                    <p>Architecture supports scaling to thousands of catalog records without affecting browser rendering speeds.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="neon-card">
                    <h4 style="color:var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">🔒 Security</h4>
                    <p>Protected REST controllers utilizing stateless JWT, crypt-hashed passwords, and structured CORS rules.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="neon-card">
                    <h4 style="color:var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">📱 Usability</h4>
                    <p>Responsive design prioritizing mobile viewports, using high contrast styles and accessible inputs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Analysis Diagram Placeholder -->
