                    <span class="bug-card-icon">🐞</span>
                    <h4>Filter State Retention Defect</h4>
                    <p><strong>Bug:</strong> Active filter parameters were not resetting when switching categories, displaying blank cells.<br><strong>Solution:</strong> Embedded cleanup dispatch handlers inside React's `useEffect` hooks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="neon-card bug-card">
                    <span class="bug-card-icon">🐞</span>
                    <h4>MongoDB Cold-Start Failure</h4>
                    <p><strong>Bug:</strong> Server database connections would periodically timeout on cold environment starts.<br><strong>Solution:</strong> Appended optimized `serverSelectionTimeoutMS` variables inside database connection configurations.</p>
                </div>
