                    <span class="bug-card-icon">🐞</span>
                    <h4>JWT Expiry Unhandled Crash</h4>
                    <p><strong>Bug:</strong> Admin authentication tokens expiring without notice caused raw network failure messages.<br><strong>Solution:</strong> Programmed Axios token interceptors executing an automatic routing to the login interface upon 401 returns.</p>
                </div>
